Body: Description: Is there a means to define the Stale parameter for the File System module to not just one year but possibly to 8, 9 or 10 years? Or can a report be configure to pull data based on a modified stale date parameter?
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Frantz Baptiste, Kevin Moore
What We've Learned Updated: The customer needs to manipulate the Stale Content data to display more than one year of Stale data.
